English
Description & requirements
Description
We’re CX fanatics, as passionate about our clients as their fans are. It’s why the most-loved brands in the world rely on us. You'll find us behind the brilliance of category-redefining fintechs, technology legends, and more. Now, we are looking for an English speaking Customer Service Representative who loves helping others and deeply cares about providing excellent customer service. And we want you to join us!
What's in it for YOU!
International and inclusive environment, that makes you feel supported, encouraged, and welcome from day one;
Continuous development through our internal learning platforms and external training;
Endless growth opportunities: 90% of our managers and leaders started their careers as customer service specialists;
2-3 weeks training course that will introduce you to the specifics of the job;
Modern and comfortable office and relaxing spaces to take a break;
Flexible work schedule;
Free taxi rides for shifts ending between 7:30PM and 11PM;
Corporate benefits and discounts.
Join Transcom as a Customer service representative !
Be on the front line of support for clients and deliver impactful work on a company level. In this role, you will:
Work for a leading car rental agency, assisting international customers with their mobility needs (reservations, modifications, assistance);
Provide high-quality assistance (English) by answering calls professionally, warmly, and efficiently;
Manage various situations: from booking reservations and handling contracts to logistical support and problem-solving;
Contribute to the project’s success by suggesting process improvements and sharing knowledge with your team;
Work on a rotational shift schedule.
